kr.pe.codda.client.connection.asyn

Class AsynThreadSafeSingleConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • kr.pe.codda.client.connection.asyn.AsynThreadSafeSingleConnection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsynConnectionIF, ClientIOEventHandlerIF, ConnectionIF, ReceivedMiddleObjectForwarderIF

    public class AsynThreadSafeSingleConnection
extends java.lang.Object
implements AsynConnectionIF, ClientIOEventHandlerIF, ReceivedMiddleObjectForwarderIF
    쓰레드 세이프한 비동기 단일 연결, 폴에 소속되지 않고 개별적 요청시 생성된다.
    Author:
    Won Jonghoon
